title: Quiet Renovated Townhome in Plymouth - Fernbrook Townhomes
posting_body: ['Fernbrook Townhomes - Fully Renovated 3 Bedroom Townhome', 'Property Address', '14254 43rd Ave N - D | Plymouth, MN 55446', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Fernbrook Townhomes in Plymouth, MN, offer a great step up from apartment living.', 'The property is located in the heart of Plymouth close to shopping, local dining, and great parks and trails!', "You'll enjoy having more space, a yard, and a garage without the troubles of home ownership while staying close to Downtown Minneapolis!", 'Lawn care, snow removal, and general maintenance are all included in the rent.', 'With three large bedrooms, two bathrooms, in-unit laundry, and an attached 2-car garage you will love this townhome after it has been given a full renovation!', 'We will be replacing all flooring, cabinetry, countertops, and appliances to make this home new!', 'You will also love your private walkout patio and outdoor space to relax!', 'Pets are welcome with a $200 refundable deposit and a $200 non-refundable pet fee.', 'Pets have a monthly fee of $35/cat, and $50 for a pet dog with a one-dog limit per unit (some breed restrictions).', '$150 Admin Fee', 'County: Hennepin, School District: 281 Robbinsdale', 'This townhouse will not last long!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'today to schedule your private tour!', 'Note: Photos are a representation of the property and not the specific photos for the advertised apartment.', 'Amenities', 'Patio', 'Attached Garage', 'In-Unit Full Size Washer and Dryer', 'Central Air-Conditioning', 'Lawn Care and Snow Removal Included', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,200', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,395.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
